GIVEAWAY!! Win a @typesauto Dash Cam and a signed @shophailiedeegan merch shirt 🙌. Or you can buy a Dash Cam you can use code “DASH15” on @typesauto website for a discount!! #TypeS #typesauto

Follow these simple steps to win!

➡️ Tag 3 friends in the comments. The more friends you tag the better. 

➡️ Follow @typesauto – this will be checked! 

➡️ Comment #dashcam on @typesauto last photo
